@MiniAuthSystem_HostAddress = http://localhost:5130

### 測試公開端點 - 健康檢查
GET {{MiniAuthSystem_HostAddress}}/api/public/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 測試公開端點 - 系統資訊
GET {{MiniAuthSystem_HostAddress}}/api/public/info
Accept: application/json

###

### 用戶註冊
POST {{MiniAuthSystem_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 用戶登入
POST {{MiniAuthSystem_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 訪問受保護端點 - 需要 JWT Token (請將 YOUR_JWT_TOKEN 替換為實際的 Token)
GET {{MiniAuthSystem_HostAddress}}/api/protected/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###

### 訪問受保護端點 - 獲取資料
GET {{MiniAuthSystem_HostAddress}}/api/protected/data
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
